  "description": "cAdvisor: do not use `image!=\"\"` — cAdvisor often omits `image` or leaves it empty, so that matcher drops every series. CPU/memory use `job=\"cadvisor\"` plus `name!=\"/\"` and `name!=\"/docker\"`. Memory panels divide Prometheus byte counters by 1024² so Grafana shows MiB.",
